{"tid":619534,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔準菲傭同我老公講野，有犯法咩？","createTime":"2018-04-06T17:23:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-08T18:28:05.000Z","uid":82845,"like":39,"dislike":2692,"uniUserReply":116,"replies":[{"pid":"9a21a28fac6c578904e29e4906e6c8cab5079f5b","tid":619534,"uid":82845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T17:23:01.000Z","msg":"由我屋企day 1請菲傭開始, 我就有規矩, 唔准佢直接同我老公講野<br />\n<br />\n有任何野,同我講就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n相反老公有野叫菲傭做都係透過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n初期有時個姐姐會犯規(其實應該有心試我底線), 我會當做錯野咁鬧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n後來慢慢就好左, 一直都相安無事<br />\n<br />\n尋日同個朋友講起, 佢話我侵犯個菲傭人權, 大家搞到有D唔愉快<br />\n<br />\nbtw我認為我冇犯法, 我係一家之主, 規矩我定係冇問題<br />\n<br />\n大家評評理"},{"pid":"459b64f4d2b3bbc018da7ced78f528d0a65c83f6","tid":619534,"uid":138197,"like":2554,"dislike":10,"score":2544,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T17:23:45.000Z","msg":"死撚番去babykingdom pls"},{"pid":"51a47d85d591a1906585b87ccbb76ba6b2797c9c","tid":619534,"uid":19072,"like":934,"dislike":6,"score":928,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T17:24:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0f75ef311b720ea744eedc7dc3e909df43dcbfdc","tid":619534,"uid":62028,"like":190,"dislike":0,"score":190,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T17:24:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/W4OdccqvIDM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FW4OdccqvIDM&d=e9JVnQrpDxgtJAA6IbMN9NibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=448521ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/W4OdccqvIDM</a>"},{"pid":"f4aa98d46629f02ec3197a1acdf3996f78a5ade0","tid":619534,"uid":54884,"like":370,"dislike":10,"score":360,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T17:24:58.000Z","msg":"完全認同啦 仲要唔可以有眼神接觸 任何溝通互動都唔應該有"},{"pid":"6c565195cfcb1aa7f57e084a1e50fa63ebe49442","tid":619534,"uid":33495,"like":10,"dislike":33,"score":-23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T17:25:28.000Z","msg":"啱啊，十